  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">6: Memo</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;"><image src="6r.gif" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image> Memo dialog</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="VariableName">Memo</text> is a <text styleclass="VariableName">Windows NotePad® </text>style interface.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Interface">Model-Editor</text> and<text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> all </text><text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editors</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> can have their own </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Memo</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">. We save</text> the <text styleclass="VariableName">Memo</text> for you with the model file.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">In the default case, the <text styleclass="VariableName">Memo</text> opens each time you start <text styleclass="VariableName">MechDesigner</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">To disable the <text styleclass="VariableName">Memo</text> when you start <text styleclass="VariableName" translate="false">MechDesigner</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">:</text></para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Clear the <text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-style:normal;">Automatically Open on Start</text> check-box, at the bottom of the interface <image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:bold;">.</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><image src="MD-Dialog-Memo.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Memo dialog]]></caption></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">To open a <text styleclass="VariableName">Memo</text> at any other time.</para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Right-click the</text>&#32;<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Mechanism-Tab" styleclass="Interface">Model name-tab</link> or any <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Mechanism-Tab" styleclass="Interface">Mechanism name-tab</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text>&#32;<text styleclass="T_Menu">Open Memo</text> in the shortcut menu.</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
